hadiths[33]{hadithnumber,text}:
3591,"Hazrat Salma bin Nufel kindi (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas betha tha ke eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! logon ney ghodon ko ahmiyat dena chhod di hai aur unhoney hathiyar rakh diye hain aur wo kehney lagey hain : ab jihad nahin raha. jang khatam ho chuki hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apna chehra anwar logon ki taraf kya aur irshad farmaya : wo ghalat kehtey hain. jihad to ab farz huwa hai aur meri ummat ka eik azeem giroh haq ( ko ghalib karney ) key liye ladta rahega. Allah Taala un sey ladney key liye bahut sey logon key dil kufr ki taraf maael karta rahega aur Allah Taala unhen un sey rizq ata farmata rahega yahan tak ke qiyamat qaaim ho jaey aur Allah Taala ka (ghalbey wala ) wada pura ho jaey. aur ( jihad ki niyat sey rakhey gaey ) ghodon ki peshaniyon mein qiyamat tak key liye khair rakh di gaee hai. mujhey wahi ki gaee hai ke main duniya mein rehney wala nahin balke un-qareeb faut ho jaaunga, aur tum merey baad girohon mein bat jaaogey aur eik dusrey ki gardanen kaatogey. aur (qurbe-qiyamat fitnon key daur mein) eman walon ka asal markaz Sham hoga."
3592,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat tak key liye ( jihad key liye rakhey gaey ) ghodon ki peshaniyon mein khair rakh di gaee hai. ghodey teen qism key hotey hain : kuch to aadmi key liye sawab ka zaria hain, kuch parda poshi ka kaam detey hain aur kuch gunah ka sabab hain. sawab to us shakhs key liye hai jo unhen jihad fi sabililah key liye waqf kar deta hai balke wo unhen paalta hi jihad key liye hai. aisey ghodey jo bhi apney pet mein dalen, uskey iwaz mein us shakhs key liye sawab likha jata hai aur agar koi charagah samney aa jaey … الخ ."
3593,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ghodey kisi shakhs key liye sawab ka zaria hain, kisi key liye parda poshi ka sabab hain aur kisi key liye gunah ka moojib hain. sawab us shakhs key liye hain jisney unhen jihad key liye baandh rakha hai aur charagah aur baghichey mein unki rassi faraakh kar rakhi hai. wo rassi mein bandhey huye us charagah aur baghichey sey jo kuch bhi khaeyn piyengey, wo uskey liye nekiyan hi nekiyan hain. aur agar wo rassi tuda kar eik do tiley tak idhar-udhar bhag jaeyn to unkey nishaanaat qadam yahan tak ke un ki leed bhi uski nekiyon mein izaafey ka sabab hai aur agar wo kisi nehar aur darya key paas sey guzartey waqt pani pi lein, chahey us ney unhen pani pilaney ka irada na kya ho, to wo pani bhi uskey liye nekiyan ban jaeyga. ye to sawab waley ghodey hain. aur jis aadmi ney unhen apney faaeydey key liye baandha ke kisi key samney daste-sawal daraz na karna padey, uskey sath sath us ney un ghodon aur un ki sawari key masley mein Allah Taala ka haq bhula nahin diya, ye us shakhs key liye parda posh hain. aur jis shakhs ney fakhr, riyakari aur ehale-Islam ki mukhalifat ki gharz sey ghodey baandhey, to ye uskey liye gunah ka moojib hongey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey gadhey ( paalney ) key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : unkey barey mein mujh par koi makhsus wahi to nahin utri, albatta ye wahid jamey aayat mojud hai : « { فَمَنْ یَّعْمَلْ مِثْقَالَ ذَرَّۃٍ }  jo shakhs zarra bhar neki kerega, uski jaza pa lega aur jo zarra bhar burai kerega, uski saza pa lega."
3594,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko biwiyon key baad koi chiz ghodon sey badh kar mehbub nahin thi.
3595,"Hazrat Abu-Wahab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai … aur wo sahabi they … ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : anbiya Alaihimussalam key naam apnao Allah azz-w-jall ko sab sey ziyada piyarey naam Abdullah aur Abdur-Rehman hain. ( jihad key liye) ghodey rakha karo aur ( piyaar sey) un ki peshaniyon aur pushton par haath pheraa karo. unkey galey mein haar dala karo lekin tundi na dalo, neez qurmuzi rang key ghodey rakha karo jin ki peshani aur haath paaun safed hon ya isi tarah key surkh ya siyah ghodey rakho. (yani un ki peshani aur haath paaun safed hon)."
3596,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ghodey mein shikaal ko pasand nahin farmatey they. alfaz Ismail bin Masood key hain.
3597,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ghodey mein shikaal ko napasand farmaya hai. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman ( Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ) bayan kartey hain ke shikaal ye hai ke teen paaun to safed hon magar eik aam rang ka ho. ya teen paaun aam rang key hon aur eik safed ho, neez shikaal paaun mein hota hai, haathon mein nahin."
3598,"Hazrat Salim key walid mohtaram (Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen chizon mein nahusat ho sakti hai : aurat, ghoda aur ghar."
3599,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ghar, aurat aur ghodey mein nahusat mumkin hai."
3600,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar nahusat ka wajood hai, to wo ghar, ghodey aur aurat mein ho sakti hai."
3601,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ghodon ki peshaniyon mein barkat rakh di gaee hai."
3602,"Hazrat Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap apney ghodey ki peshani key baal apni do ungliyon key darmiyan bat rahey they aur farma rahey they : ghodon ki peshaniyon mein qiyamat tak key liye khair rakh di gaee hai, yani sawab aur ghanimat."
3603,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat tak key liye ghodon ki peshaniyon mein khair hai.
3604,Hazrat Urwa Barqi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ghodon ki peshaniyon mein qiyamat tak key liye khair rakh di gaee hai.
3605,"Hazrat Urwa bin abi Jaad (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : ghodon ki peshaniyon mein qiyamat tak key liye khair rakh di gaee hai, yani sawab aur maale-ghanimat."
3606,"Hazrat Urwa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : qiyamat tak key liye ghodon ki peshaniyon mein khair rakh di gaee hai, yani sawab aur maal ghanimat."
3607,"Hazrat Urwa bin abi Jaad (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat tak ghodon ki peshaniyon mein khair rakh di gaee hai, yani sawab aur ghanimat."
3608,"Hazrat Khalid bin Yazid Johni sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) merey paas sey guzartey to farmatey : Khalid! aao bahar ja kar teer andazi karen. eik din mujhey zara der ho gaee to farmaney lagey : Khalid aao main tumhen wo baat batata hun jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaai hai. main unkey paas pahuncha to farmaney lagey : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala eik teer ki wajeh sey teen ashkhaas ko jannat mein dakhil farmaeyga : eik to teer bananey wala , jo teer banatey waqt achi (jihad ya sawab ki) niyat rakhta hai. doosra teer phainkney wala, aur teesra teer pakdaaney wala. teer andazi ( ki mashq ) kya karo aur sawari (ki mashq) kya karo. aur merey nazdik teer andazi ghod sawari sey ziyada pasandida hai. mustahab khel sirf teen hain : aadmi apney ghodey ko tarbiyat dey ya apni biwi sey dil lagi karey ya apney teer kamaan sey teer andazi ( ki mashq ) kerey. jis aadmi ney teer andazi seekhney key baad usey ahmiyat na detey huye chhod diya to usney ( Allah Taala ki ) nemat ki nashukri ki."
3609,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har Arbi ghodey ko raat key aakhiri hissey mein do dafa us dua ki ijazat di jati hai, aey Allah ! tu ney insanon mein sey jis shakhs ko mera Malik banaya hai aur mujhey uskey sath khas kya hai, uskey yahan mujhey uskey ehal o maal mein sey mehbub tareen chiz bana dey."
3610,Hazrat Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko eik khachar tohfey mein mila. aap is par sawar huye. mainey kaha : agar hum ghodi ko gadhey sey jufti karwa lein to hamarey paas bhi is jaisa khachar ho jaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye kaam to be ilm aur jahil log kartey hain.
3611,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Ubedullah bin Abbas sey riwayat hai ke main Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) key paas betha tha. itney main eik aadmi ney un sey puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Zohar aur Asr ki namaz mein qirat farmatey they? unhoney kaha : nahin. us aadmi ney kaha : mumkin hai ke aap dil mein padhtey hon? wo kehney lagey : Allah karey to zakhmi ho. ye to pehli sey buri baat hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key bandey they. Allah Taala ney aap ko jo bhi ehkam diye, aap ney aagey pahuncha diye. Allah ki qism ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hum (ehle-bait) ko logon sey alag koi khususi hukm nahin diya magar ye teen cheezen (hon to hon) : aap ney hamen hukm diya ke hum wuzu achi tarah keren, hum sadqa na khaeyn aur ghodi ko gadhey sey juftii na karaein."
3612,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney Allah key raastey mein ghoda waqf kya, Allah Taala par eman rakhtey huye aur uskey wada sawab ki tasdeeq kartey huye to us ghodey ka khana-peena, peshab o gobar uskey tarazu mein nekiyon ka zaria ban jaeyngey."
3613,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ghodon mein dod karwai. aap ney in ko hafiya sey saniya al-wadaa tak daudaaya aur jin ghodon ko daud key liye tayyar nahin kya gaya tha, unkey darmiyan Saniya al-wadaa sey masjid banu Zureq tak daud karwai."
3614,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney tazmir shuda ghodon key darmiyan Hafiya sey Saniya al-wadaa tak daud ka muqabla karwaya aur un ghodon ko jin ki tazmir nahin ki gaee thi, Saniya al-wadaa sey banu Zureq ki masjid tak daudaaya Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney bhi us muqabley mein hissa liya tha."
3615,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teerandazi, ghud-daud aur oont daud key ilawa kisi muqabley mein inaam ( muqarrar karna ya hasil karna ) durust nahin."
3616,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teer andazi, ghud-daud aur oont-daud key ilawa kisi chiz mein inaam nahin rakha ja sakta."
3617,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke oont dorr ya ghud-daud key ilawa kisi muqabley mein inaam muqarrar karna halal aur jayez nahin.
3618,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki eik oontni thi jisey azba kaha jata tha. us sey koi oont aagey nahin badh sakta tha. eik Erabi (dehati) apney jawan oont par aaya aur us sey muqabley mein aagey badh gaya. ye baat musalmanon ko bahut nagawar guzri. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey chehron key tassurat dekhey jabkey wo keh rahey they : aey Allah key Rasool ! azba to peechey reh gaee ! to aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney ye baat lazim qarar dey li hai ke duniya ki jo chiz bhi buland martaba hogi, Allah Taala usey ( kisi na kisi waqt ) neecha dikhaye."
3619,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : oonton aur ghodon key ilawa deegar janweron mein daud ka inaami muqabla nahin karwaya ja sakta.
3620,"Hazrat Imran bin Husein (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Islam mein jalb, janb aur nikah shighaar ki koi gunjaaish nahin. aur jo shakhs daka daley, wo hum mein sey nahin."
3621,"Hazrat Imran bin Husein (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Islam mein jalb, janb aur nikah wata ki ijazat nahin."
3622,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik Erabi (dehati) ney (apney oont par) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ( ki oontni ) sey daud ka muqabla kya. wo aap sey aagey badh gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum goya us bina par ghamgin o afsurda sey ho gaey. aap sey ye baat kahi gaee to aap ney farmaya : Allah Taala ney ye lazim kar liya hai ke jo chiz bhi duniya mein apney aap ko ooncha keregi, aakhir-kar Allah Taala usey neecha dikhayega."
3623,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) farmaya kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney jang khaibar mein walid mohtaram Hazrat Zuber bin Awam (Raziallahu anhu) ko chaar hissey diye they. eik unka apna, doosra aap ka rishtey daar honey ki wajeh sey kyonkey abdul-Muttalib ki beti Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anha) Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ki walida thin aur baqi do hissey ghodey key."
